üìå WORKFLOWS TO IMPLEMENT
================================================================================

User Workflow:
1. User enters a dish name OR uploads menu photo
2. OCR extracts dish names
3. Ingredients parsed by AI
4. Interaction engine assigns risk levels
5. System shows safe alternative dishes
6. User can generate a 7-day AI meal plan
7. Optional: send data to doctor dashboard

Doctor Workflow:
1. Doctor logs in
2. Sees patient risk history
3. Views past dish scans + interactions
4. Downloads clinical report

